data.description: This home is ready for you to move in.This 2 bedroom/2 bathroom split floor plan sits on a double lot and has 2 Arizona rooms. The home has numerous updates such as newer AC unit,  hot water heater, dishwasher,  washer/dryer, interior/exterior paint and even a reverse osmosis.The large lot is fully fenced and has beautiful oleanders (on drip system) around it that provide a wall of privacy.  Florence Gardens is an active 55+ community that offers numerous amenities such as a large clubhouse that hosts bingo, dinners and activities.There are 2 pools, spa and even a 9 hole golf course. We are located in the charming town of Florence which has numerous restaurants and even a winery. There is a mature Tangelo & Pink Grapefruit tree.The home is being sold furnished and ready for its new owners
